page.title: 09Tracey's Diary 15/5/85
page.content: 07.33: Dressed; read "Bird Life"; played Hangman on the computer. 07.49: Dad arrived home from night shift at Bowater-Scott. Breakfast of home made muesli and orange juice. 08.07: Washed, got ready for school. 08.20: Listened to Abba tape at friend's house, went to school. 09.05: Assembly, Bible quiz, Class 2 09.25: Mental Arithmetic test on area. 09.44: Maths. 10.35: Playtime. I stayed in to clear cupboard. 10.50: English. 12.00: Dinner break- egg and bacon flan, salad and semolina with chocolate 13.15: Drew a picture of friend for Assembly. 14.15: Playtime. 14.30 Continued drawing. 15.00: Listened to story. 15.30: Home time. 15.45: Helped prepare tea of savoury flan, carrots, peas and cake. 17.00: Ice-skating with my sister. 19.00: Went home. 21.00: Went to bed.
